---
title: "_setAuction (AuctionBidder)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_zero: auction == address(0)
    q_check_zero --> q_revert_zero: true
    q_check_zero --> q_check_interface: false
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroAddress()
    q_check_interface --> q_revert_interface: !supportsInterface(IBaseAuction.interfaceId)
    q_check_interface --> q_check_same: supportsInterface(IBaseAuction.interfaceId)
    q_revert_interface --> [*]: revert InvalidAuctionContract(auction)
    q_check_same --> q_revert_same: address(s_auction) == auction
    q_check_same --> q_set: address(s_auction) != auction
    q_revert_same --> [*]: revert ValueNotUpdated()
    q_set --> q_emit: s_auction = IBaseAuction(auction)
    q_emit --> [*]: emit AuctionContractSet(auction)

    note right of q_check_zero
        INV-001: auction address must not be zero
    end note

    note right of q_check_interface
        INV-002: auction must implement IBaseAuction interface (ERC-165 check)
    end note

    note right of q_check_same
        INV-003: new auction must differ from current auction (no redundant updates)
    end note
